\s Kujeni kusifu na furaha
\zon1 4
\zoli1 \bd Kujeni kusifu na furaha nyingi, Kujeni kusifu Yesu ndiye Mwokozi\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Alizaliwa kuwa Mukombozi.\bd*
\pc \bdit Kujeni kumwabudu, kujeni kumwabudu, Kujeni kumwabudu Yesu Mwokozi.\bdit*
