\zoli1 \bd Pamoja na jeshi la\bd*\bd  Mbingu\bd*\bd ni juu Tusifu na kuabudu Yesu daima\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Mwana wa \bd*\bd Mungu\bd*\bd  anapata mwili.\bd*
